<p style="line-height: 40px;">
    Privacy Policy for EasyBook

    Effective Date: 22.06.2023

    This Privacy Policy describes how EasyBook collects, uses, and discloses personal information when you use our web application. We are committed to protecting the privacy and security of your personal information.

    Information We Collect
    1.1 Personal Information
    When you use our Service, we may collect the following types of personal information:

    Name
    Email address
    Contact information (such as address, phone number)
    Login credentials (username and password)
    Usage data (such as your interactions with the Service, preferences, and settings)
    Device information (such as IP address, browser type, operating system)
